The only formal way to move up the grade entails what the employer calls ‘interview’. These interviews are conducted irregularly once in a while and the teachers must apply to be considered.
Rape allegation
There were times they would travel to Nairobi for the same, but these days, the exercise is localised while the teachers are, ironically, delocalised. The questions during the interviews can come from anywhere and be about anything.



